Package cams.users

Class Staff

java.lang.Object
cams.users.User
cams.users.Staff
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Staff extends User implements Serializable
Represents a staff member specialisation of User. Object is Serializable. Staff members have specific functionalities related to managing camps including processing enquiries and suggestions.
